### Calculate value change from 2020 to 2022 (POST)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_year": 2020,
  "end_year": 2022
}

### Calculate value change from 2020 to 2025 (POST) - Forward calculation
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_year": 2020,
  "end_year": 2025
}

### Calculate value change from 2025 to 2020 (POST) - Backward calculation
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "start_year": 2025,
  "end_year": 2020
}

### Calculate value change using GET method - 2020 to 2022
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change?start_year=2020&end_year=2022

