GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change?start_year=2019&end_year=2024

### Calculate value change using GET method - Backward (2024 to 2020)
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/inflation/value-change?start_year=2024&end_year=2020

